h2.heading.heading--secondary#dropzone Dropzone
p.paragraph.
  The dropzone is the initial state of every fileupload and should be used wherever possible.  If a file upload is not feasible, a classic file upload should be used.

.example
  include ../includes/example-header.jade
  .example__content
    .example__border
      iframe.example__iframe(
        src=relative('/components/form-and-input-elements/demos/fileupload-dropzone.html')
        data-iframe-resizer
      )

.toggle
